  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/c84bafe3b5e704548f686317cac5ad44.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/c84bafe3b5e704548f686317cac5ad44.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/c84bafe3b5e704548f686317cac5ad44.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gilly, the owner of a local arcade, is trying to save his business from a faceless mega-corporation, Fun Fun Co. ...and what better way to stick it to the man than with a brand-spanking-new super game. Unfortunately, the corp gets wind of Gilly’s plan and launches a cyberattack, injecting a virus into the game. Now it’s up to you, will you rise up to save both the game and the last remaining local arcade?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/366e227aa9f5d3253a84a3a775867307.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/366e227aa9f5d3253a84a3a775867307.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/366e227aa9f5d3253a84a3a775867307.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This ever-evolving co-op multiplayer, roguelite shooter allows you and up to 3 friends to explore multiple biomes, compete in mini games, find hidden chests, and battle a crazy cast of enemies and bosses.  Speed into the action or take it slow, it’s up to you. As you get to know the town, you can dive into additional challenges from the local gangs that hangout in Gilly’s Arcade, earning you much more than just street cred. Though, the view from the top of the leaderboards must be pretty darn good...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/abde826aa876b863a333c7e3e1e9f4e6.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/abde826aa876b863a333c7e3e1e9f4e6.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/de347083cb48de76252965b0433251ad.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/de347083cb48de76252965b0433251ad.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/de347083cb48de76252965b0433251ad.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/5e29c2b2012ee06e97dd87e144841942.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/5e29c2b2012ee06e97dd87e144841942.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/5e29c2b2012ee06e97dd87e144841942.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/c84bafe3b5e704548f686317cac5ad44.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/c84bafe3b5e704548f686317cac5ad44.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/c84bafe3b5e704548f686317cac5ad44.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gilly, the owner of a local arcade, is trying to save his business from a faceless mega-corporation, Fun Fun Co. ...and what better way to stick it to the man than with a brand-spanking-new super game. Unfortunately, the corp gets wind of Gilly’s plan and launches a cyberattack, injecting a virus into the game. Now it’s up to you, will you rise up to save both the game and the last remaining local arcade?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/366e227aa9f5d3253a84a3a775867307.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/366e227aa9f5d3253a84a3a775867307.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/366e227aa9f5d3253a84a3a775867307.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This ever-evolving co-op multiplayer, roguelite shooter allows you and up to 3 friends to explore multiple biomes, compete in mini games, find hidden chests, and battle a crazy cast of enemies and bosses.  Speed into the action or take it slow, it’s up to you. As you get to know the town, you can dive into additional challenges from the local gangs that hangout in Gilly’s Arcade, earning you much more than just street cred. Though, the view from the top of the leaderboards must be pretty darn good...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/abde826aa876b863a333c7e3e1e9f4e6.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/abde826aa876b863a333c7e3e1e9f4e6.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/de347083cb48de76252965b0433251ad.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/de347083cb48de76252965b0433251ad.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/de347083cb48de76252965b0433251ad.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/5e29c2b2012ee06e97dd87e144841942.poster.avif?t=1773153435\" width=650 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/5e29c2b2012ee06e97dd87e144841942.webm?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515640/extras/5e29c2b2012ee06e97dd87e144841942.mp4?t=1773153435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
